人。請說明你將如何處理這種情況與進行個案諮商的方法。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "74bd2dd97b1e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112130", "c": "111", "s": "0804", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "諮商與輔導", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "心理輔導員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-8cba2e09-moex-00041', 'judicial-8cba2e09', 'judicial-8cba2e09-moex-112-696aa37c', 'sub-judicial-8cba2e09-03', NULL, 'essay', '性平三法內涵為何？高三青少年乙女向你投訴國小五年級時導師見其
